P.S. an informal guide to the physics major course by Prof. T. Watari(IPMU) https://member.ipmu.jp/taizan.watari/inf_guide.html
1. 有两种常用的英文项目，且可以同时申请，参见 (https://www.s.u-tokyo.ac.jp/en/admission/)
2. an informal guide to the physics major course by Prof. T. Watari(IPMU) https://member.ipmu.jp/taizan.watari/inf_guide.html
3. **需要在申请前确定导师，且入学后换导师的可能性较小。**

## Special Selection for International Applicants (Master's and Doctoral Programs)

1. 网页：https://www.s.u-tokyo.ac.jp/en/admission/graduate.html
2. 只能申请硕士
3. 申请材料：
```
      1）网上的申请表
      2）需要GRE subject成绩，不需要GRE General
      3）托福成绩
      4）成绩单和毕业证明
      5）Payment Confirmation of the Application Fee（Monbukagakusho Scholarship Student or an Embassy Recommended Monbukagakusho Scholarship Candidate不需要）
      6）Personal Statement (1 or 2 pages of A4-size paper, in English, single space, in any format): Please describe what you have studied, what research you have conducted, and your other activities. Give detailed descriptions of the things you wish to emphasize in order to show your abilities, self-initiative, conviction, etc.
      7）Statement of Purpose (1 or 2 pages of A4-size paper, in English, single space, in any format): Please describe the research content you wish to conduct at the Graduate School of Science. Give detailed descriptions of your motivations for conducting research in the specific field and, if possible, your research plan, by explaining the specific research field and specifying the name(s) of the potential supervising professor(s) you wish to study under.
      8）Proof of your prior consultation with the potential supervising professor(s) at the Graduate School of Science, such as a copy of correspondence emails
      9）推荐信：Two recommendation letters from your current supervisors or individuals who are familiar with your academic or scientific work. Please enter the referees' names, organizations, positions and email addresses on the Application Form on the website. Our system will automatically send emails to the referees asking them to fill out our recommendation form. The referees will then have to access the designated URLs to fill out the form.
```
4. 申请时间：推荐第一个
![](https://github.com/XiaoweiOu/Info-for-Graduate-School-Application/blob/master/picture/ApplicationTime-UTokyo.png)
5. Admission decision：同上，考虑第一个
![](https://github.com/XiaoweiOu/Info-for-Graduate-School-Application/blob/master/picture/AdmissionTime-UTokyo.png)
6. 费用：
![](https://github.com/XiaoweiOu/Info-for-Graduate-School-Application/blob/master/picture/Fee-UTokyo.png)
**To do**
- 奖学金 https://www.s.u-tokyo.ac.jp/en/offices/ilo/scholarship.html
